Primi generis, which the Church made vse of, although Illust. they received them not in the Canon: as the 
Macchabees, Iesus Syrach, the Wisedome of Salomon, Tobie;
Rufinus in Symbolum. These were not called Canonici by the Fathers, but Ecclesiastici.


